        "liquid_3BF6VF": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<div style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n  <!-- SLIDES WRAPPER -->\n  <div id=\"review-track\" style=\"display: flex; transition: transform 0.4s ease; will-change: transform;\">\n\n    <!-- AVIS 1 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/Screenshot_2026-02-06_at_8.56.23_AM_430x.png?v=1773259151\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">Alejandro M.</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Era escéptico total. Ya había probado magnesio, vitamina B12, matcha... nada duraba más de una semana. Llevo 3 semanas con el parche y he reducido a 1 café al día. La diferencia a las 15h es brutal — sigo concentrado sin ningún crash.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 2 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/2c540bcf-9536-4b6f-bb27-e8eed0265cfc_430x.png?v=1773259153\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">Carlos D.</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Mi primera duda era si se vería en la oficina. No se nota absolutamente nada bajo la camisa. Lo llevo cada día en reuniones, nadie sabe nada. Y lo mejor — las reuniones de las 4 de la tarde ya no me cuestan como antes.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 3 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/Screenshot_2026-02-06_at_8.55.50_AM_430x.png?v=1773259150\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">David P.</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Investigué los ingredientes antes de comprarlo — Mucuna Pruriens, Rhodiola, 5-HTP, todo natural. Aun así dudé. Al final me convenció la garantía de devolución. Dos semanas después pedí ya el bote de 2 meses. No vuelvo a los Red Bulls.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- NAVIGATION -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-top: 14px;\">\n    <button onclick=\"reviewSlide(-1)\" style=\"background: none; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; color: #374151;\">‹</button>\n    <div id=\"review-dots\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 6px;\">\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(0)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #FACC15; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(1)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d1d5db; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(2)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d1d5db; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n    </div>\n    <button onclick=\"reviewSlide(1)\" style=\"background: none; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; color: #374151;\">›</button>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  var reviewCurrent = 0;\n  var reviewTotal = 3;\n\n  function reviewGoTo(index) {\n    reviewCurrent = index;\n    document.getElementById('review-track').style.transform = 'translateX(-' + (reviewCurrent * 100) + '%)';\n    var dots = document.getElementById('review-dots').children;\n    for (var i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {\n      dots[i].style.background = i === reviewCurrent ? '#FACC15' : '#d1d5db';\n    }\n  }\n\n  function reviewSlide(dir) {\n    reviewCurrent = (reviewCurrent + dir + reviewTotal) % reviewTotal;\n    reviewGoTo(reviewCurrent);\n  }\n</script>"
          }
