    "custom_liquid_UhArkr": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div style=\"margin: 24px 0; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin: 16px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">Preguntas frecuentes</h3>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 1 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Cuánto tarda en hacer efecto?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">La mayoría nota el efecto en 20–30 minutos tras aplicar el parche. El pico de energía llega aproximadamente a la hora. Para resultados estables y duraderos, recomendamos usarlo al menos 30 días seguidos.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 2 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Se nota el parche bajo la ropa?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">No. El parche es ultra-fino, color piel y sin olor. Bajo una camisa o camiseta es completamente invisible. Puedes llevarlo en reuniones, presentaciones o en el gimnasio — nadie sabrá que lo llevas.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 3 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Es como un Red Bull o una bebida energética?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">No. Sin cafeína, sin taurina, sin azúcar. Los ingredientes (Mucuna Pruriens, Rhodiola Rosea, 5-HTP) apoyan tu producción natural de dopamina. Energía estable durante 8h, sin picos ni crash posterior.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 4 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Ya probé magnesio, B12, ashwagandha — ¿por qué esto sería diferente?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">La diferencia está en la vía de absorción. Las cápsulas pasan por el sistema digestivo y pierden entre un 30–50% de su potencia. El parche transdérmico actúa directamente en el torrente sanguíneo — sin pérdidas, sin digestión. Es por eso que funciona cuando las pastillas no lo hacen.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 5 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Puedo usarlo junto con mi café de la mañana?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Sí. El parche complementa tu rutina actual — no obliga a cambiar nada. Muchos usuarios lo combinan con un café por la mañana y simplemente dejan de necesitar el segundo o el tercero del día.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 6 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Garantía de devolución?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">30 días de garantía total. Si no notas ninguna diferencia, te devolvemos el 100% del importe sin preguntas ni complicaciones. Escríbenos a support@nelorya.com y gestionamos el reembolso en 48h.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 7 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FACC15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">¿Cuánto tarda el envío a España?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Enviamos en 24h. Entrega en España en 7–12 días laborables. Envío gratuito a partir del primer pedido.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq2(btn) {\n    var answer = btn.nextElementSibling;\n    var arrow = btn.querySelector('.faq2-arrow');\n    var isOpen = answer.style.display === 'block';\n    answer.style.display = isOpen ? 'none' : 'block';\n    arrow.style.transform = isOpen ? 'rotate(0deg)' : 'rotate(180deg)';\n  }\n</script>",
